WITH hours AS (
    SELECT toDateTime('2024-06-15 00:00:00', 'UTC') + INTERVAL number HOUR AS hour
    FROM numbers(24)
)
SELECT
    h.hour,
    count(e.event_id) AS event_count
FROM hours h
LEFT JOIN events e
    ON toStartOfHour(e.timestamp) = h.hour
    AND toDate(e.timestamp, 'UTC') = '2024-06-15'
GROUP BY h.hour
ORDER BY h.hour
